Package: lassar-bing-wallpaper
Version: 1.0.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, curl, coreutils, findutils, wget
Maintainer: Lassar Kardival <lass@disroot.org>
Description: Automatically download and set Bing wallpapers
 A simple cross-desktop Bash utility that fetches the daily Bing wallpaper,
 sets it as your background, and cleans up older wallpapers after a week.
